data.description:
Beautiful all-brick home on a two-acre lot in the highly sought-after Bentonville School District. This 2,986 square-foot home features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 1 half bath, a bonus/game room with an updated full bathroom, a 3-car garage, and a private, fenced 0.86-acre backyard. The main level has a Master Suite with a spacious walk-in closet and a modern kitchen with new Bosch stainless appliances. Includes home seller's protection plan.
Plus, you'll love the heated and cooled workshop/man cave, pool, and covered patio on this expansive lot. It's just 3 miles west of Bentonville West High School and 10 miles north of XNA Airport, offering the perfect blend of country living and convenience.
